name: Bluedio Turbine Hurricane HT Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones -Black
short_description: DESCRIPTION  The black colored Bluedio Turbine Hurricane HT Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones are one of a kind.  They were made to please demanding users looking for a wireless headset with great audio technologies.  The HT Headphones comes with several high tech features found in today’s high end headsets, and are without a doubt one of the best wireless, high tech headsets.  They diminish the need for cables and make listening to songs a clutter free experience.  With regards to the audio performance, the HT headset is quite magnificent.  Its technology is based on 57mm ultra large dynamic drivers that deliver a well balanced sound, with clear bass, and incredible treble, which together allow you to listen to the tiniest details of a song. The noise cancelation and noise reduction features efficiently reduce ambient noise while talking or listening to music.  As far as convenience is concerned, the headset features custom fit, supra aural, soft earmuffs made of artificial protein leather to ensure long lasting comfort.  The language prompt on the HT headset comes ready with 4 languages, English, Spanish, French, and English, to make communicating easy.

name: 30000mAh Solar Power Bank Mobile Charger
short_description:
* Built-in 30000mAh high capacity rechargeable Li-Ion battery.  

* Press to charge and press it again stop charging.practical and long cycle life.Charge your mobile phone, iPod, MP3 player, GPS and more, using just sunlight and built in 30000mAh Li-ion polymer battery.

* The Solar Charge is a compact and lightweight solar charger designed for people on the move.  

* Solar Charge is designed as a backup power supply to power virtually any portable devices like Cell Phones, Smart Phones, Cameras, MP4/MP3 Players GPS and more.  

* Just place it under daylight and after the internal battery is fully charged you can supply power to any device with built in battery not exceeding more than 5V with capacity under 30000mAh.  

* Also can be charged using wall AC adapter and USB port of your computer.
 
* Using advanced solar cell and Li-ion battery technologies the Solar Charge will charge itself in all daylight conditions and will store power for times when you need as a backup power source.

How To Play:
.................................................

Insert the FM transmitter to 12V car cigarette lighter power socket. 
Insert your USB or SD device to USB/SD card jack; or  using audio-line to connect your 
MP3/MP4 to the transmitter. 
When connected, the FM transmitter plays music automatically and display shows the 
frequency (LED model) or other information (LCD model). 
Press the “CH” key to enter frequency setting mode. Press key: ‘’Next” to increase the frequency. 
Press key: ‘’Back”to decrease the frequency. Press the “CH” to quit again.
By pressing pause/play button,the music plays or pauses. Press and hold , you can choose pause/play
music playing mode–> Single loop-> All songs-> Order->Random play

name: U8 Bluetooth Smart Wrist Watch, iPhone 4/4S/5/5S, Samsung S3/S4/S5/Note 2/3/4, Android Smart phones
short_description:
Bluetooth Smart Watch Wrist Watch U8 U Watch For iPhone4/4S/5/5S Samsung S4/Note 2/Note 3 HTC Android Phone Smartphones

COLOR: WHITE

Bluetooth Smart U Watch which is compatiblewith all Bluetooth V2.0 or above enabled smartphones, tablets and PCs (supportAndroid 2.3 or above),such as iPhone 4, 4S, 5, 5S, Samsung S3, S4, Note 2, Note 3, Note 4 etc.

Features:

1.48"" Capacitive Touch Screen TFT LCD

Time / Date / Week / Battery state display

Ringing reminder when you receive a call

Ringing reminder once your mobile phone disconnected

Display the number or name of incoming calls

Answer or Dial calls from your wrist

Stopwatch function

Support hands-free calls, phone book

Play the music in your phone (after Bluetooth paring)

Sync SMS/call history (only for android phone)

Ring reminder when your Android 2.3 or above smart phonereceive a message (including Wechat,Facebook, Twitter, WhatsApp, Skype, and so on)

Anti-lost alarm function: When cellphone left watch alarmautomatically, after a certain distance to avoid lose the phones

Remote taking photo function: You can control your cellphoneto take photo from your wrist. (Only for android phone)

Altitude Meter, Passometer , Photograph, Barometer,Vibration

Specifications:

Material: Steel Silicon

Bluetooth Version: Bluetooth V3.0 EDR

Bluetooth Protocol: A2DP HFP 1.5 HS P 1.2

Range of Frequency: 2.4GHz spectrum

Ambient Noise: 75dB

Transmitting Range: 10m

Language Support: English, French, Spanish, Portuguese,Korean, Italian, German, Turkish, Russian, Japanese, Chinese

Charging Time: about 1 hour

Talk Time: about 3 hours

Music Play Time: about 6 hours

Standby Time: about 160 hours

Power Supply: Built-in 230 mAh rechargeable battery

Package includes:

1 x Bluetooth Watch

1 x USB cable

1 x User Manual

U8 U Watch: Everything you need to know (FAQ)

1. Q: Does iPhone can receive text messages on the smartwatch

A: Sorry, we don’t have an app for iPhone right now, itcannot read messages, remote capturing.

However, the other functions (call sync, address book,pedometer, calendar, stopwatch,

Calculator, alarm function, music) works well.

2. Q: Can you give instructions about how to connectBluetooth

A: First, download and install the APK in your devices(option)

Second, open Bluetooth on your devices and watch.

Third, you can use your devices to search the U8 watch, oruse U8 watch to search the device you want to match. When searching finished,please connect them by following the notice.

3. Q: Does this watch work with the Galaxy S5

A: Yes, this is a new Bluetooth Smart U Watch which iscompatible with all Bluetooth V2.0 Or above enabled smartphones (supportAndroid 2.3 or above), such as iPhone 4, 4S, 5, 5S, Samsung S3, S4, Note 2,Note 3, Note 4 etc.

4. Q: Is it water proof or water resistant

A: It is Normal waterproof; a little water is no problem.But never put it into water.

5. Q: Does the watch have internal earphone port to listenmusic

A: Sorry, it doesn’t have headphone jack, but it has its ownspeaker in it.

6. Q: Can you use this watch on Nokia windows phone

A: Sorry! It is for Android Phone & iPhone.

7. Q: Can you answer calls directly from the phone

A: yes, it supports phone answering. You also can dialthrough the watch.

8. Q: The music function of the watch only controls themusic player or does the sound come through the watch speaker too

A: Yes, it controls the music player and also the soundcomes through the watch speaker.

9. Q: When you are on the clock / watch mode, does thescreen sleep Or do I need to keep pressing the power button to know the timeof day

A: Yes, the screen will sleep. You need to press the powerbutton to know the time.

Maybe you can set the LCD backlight time according to yourrequirements.

10. Q: Is this a watch smart phone or a blue tooth watch,and does it vibrates when I get a text message

A: It is a Bluetooth watch, can connect with your smartphone, and can make it vibrate when you get a text message. But only supports Android System. (Pleaseinstall APK)

11. Q: Can this watch display a received text message foriPhone 5 I know it definitely cannot send message, but will it display Andcan it control music

A: It does not display text messages on iPhone, but you cancontrol the music.

12. Q: Does it work for tablets too

A: Sorry, it cannot!

13. Q: Can it be set to silently vibrate when you receive acall

A: Yes, you can set through Ringtone function.

14. Q: What is the battery life like on a day to day basis

A: Talk Time: about 3 hours

Music Play Time: about 6 hours

Standby Time: about 160 hours

Power Supply: Built-in 230mAh rechargeable battery

15. Q: Does it support images Can i see my photos on it

A: Sorry, it doesn’t support images.

16. Q: What’s the material of the watch Is it durableenough

A: Yes, it is of high quality. The watch band material isdurable and soft rubber.

The watch case material is stainless steel.

17. Q: How U8 working with smartphone and Bluetoothheadset If I am listening music viaBluetooth headset, can I use this watch with smartphone (receivingnotifications, Reading SMS) Or if Iconnect headset, would watch be disconnected I mean, can both devices (watchesand Bluetooth headset) working together or not (One of them needs to bedisconnected)

A: Yes, can be connected at the same time, headphones and U8both can control the mobile music. When you use Bluetooth headset listening tothe Music, U8 would show incoming calls, music will be automatically suspendeduntil the end of the phone call. Use headphones listening to music first, theconnect U8, the music will come from the U8, but headset still can control theheadset, and then the music come from the headset, and vice versa.

name: U8 Bluetooth Smart Wrist Watch - Black
short_description:
The U8 Bluetooth Smart Wrist Watch lets you stay in step with the time and the world in a new age way. This smart wrist watch features a high resolution, 1.48inch, capacitive touch display that enables you to see what matters at a glance. A high quality, black, plastic strap augments the watch’s matching black, stainless steel case further. The U8 smartwatch pairs with tablets, smartphones, and PCs that operate on Android v2.3 or higher. It is also compatible with iOS operating systems via its Bluetooth v2.0. It enables handsfree calls and gives you instant and discreet access to your mobile’s phonebook, notifications, and more. Those who have paired their Android smart devices with this accessory will also get notifications when they receive messages on WeChat, Twitter, Facebook, Skype, WhatsApp, and other such apps. Android users can also click pictures remotely with this smartwatch. An onboard passometer accurately counts the number of steps you take throughout the day. The timepiece incorporates an altitude meter, stopwatch, and barometer for your convenience.

Key Features

Bluetooth V3.0

Music Play Time: about 6 hours

Standby Time: about 160 hours

Talk Time: about 3 hours

230 mAh

Elegant, Durable Construction

This U8 watch is made using superior quality materials that look good and last long. Fine quality plastic is used in the making of its black band, which holds a matching, stainless steel case and wraps comfortably around your wrists. Atop the case is the watch’s 1.48inch, capacitive touch display that produces incredible visuals and provides at a glance information.

Multiple Functionality

This U8 smartwatch provides a ringing reminder whenever you receive a call or when your phone is disconnected from this accessory. The accessory’s anti lost alarm function can be programmed to set off automatically whenever your phone is out of its 10m transmitting range. It even displays the caller ID of the person calling you.

14. Q: What is the battery life like on a day to day basis

A: Talk Time: about 3 hours

Music Play Time: about 6 hours

Standby Time: about 160 hours

Power Supply: Built-in 230mAh rechargeable battery

15. Q: Does it support images Can i see my photos on it

A: No, it doesn't support images.

16. Q: How U8 working with smartphone and Bluetooth headset If I am listening music via Bluetooth headset, can I use this watch with smartphone (receiving notifications, Reading SMS) Or if I connect headset, would watch be disconnected I mean, can both devices (watches and Bluetooth headset) working together or not (One of them needs to be disconnected)

A: Yes, can be connected at the same time, headphones and U8 both can control the mobile music. When you use Bluetooth headset listening to the Music, U8 would show incoming calls, music will be automatically suspended until the end of the phone call. Use headphones listening to music first, the connect U8, the music will come from the U8, but headset still can control the headset, and then the music come from the headset, and vice versa
description:
Bluetooth Smart Watch Wrist Watch U8 U Watch For iPhone 4/4S/5/5S Samsung S4/Note 2/Note 3 HTC Android Phone Smartphones

COLOR: RED

This is Bluetooth Smart U Watch which is compatible with all Bluetooth V2.0 or above enabled smartphones, tablets and PCs (support Android 2.3 or above),such as iPhone 4, 4S, 5, 5S, Samsung S3, S4, Note 2, Note 3, Note 4 etc.

Features:

1- 1.48" Capacitive Touch Screen TFT LCD

2- Time / Date / Week / Battery state display

3- Ringing reminder when you receive a call

4- Ringing reminder once your mobile phone disconnected

5- Display the number or name of incoming calls

6- Answer or Dial calls from your wrist

7- Stopwatch function

8- Support hands-free calls, phone book

9- Play the music in your phone (after Bluetooth pairing)

10- Sync SMS/call history (only for android phone)

11- Ring reminder when your Android 2.3 or above smartphone receive a message (including Wechat, Facebook, Twitter, WhatsApp, Skype, and so on)

12- Anti-lost alarm function: When cellphone left watch alarm automatically, after a certain distance to avoid lose the phones

13- Remote taking photo function: You can control your cellphone to take photo from your wrist. (Only for android phone)

14- Altitude Meter, Passometer , Photograph, Barometer, Vibration

Specifications:

- Material: Steel Silicon

- Bluetooth Version: Bluetooth V3.0 EDR

- Bluetooth Protocol: A2DP HFP 1.5 HS P 1.2

- Range of Frequency: 2.4GHz spectrum

- Ambient Noise: 75dB

- Transmitting Range: 10m

- Language Support: English, French, Spanish, Portuguese, Korean, Italian, German, Turkish, Russian, Japanese, Chinese

- Charging Time: about 1 hour

- Talk Time: about 3 hours

- Music Play Time: about 6 hours

- Standby Time: about 160 hours

- Power Supply: Built-in 230 mAh rechargeable battery

Package includes:

1 x Bluetooth Watch

1 x USB cable

1 x User Manual

More Informations:

1. Q: Does iPhone can receive text messages on the smart watch

A: No, there is no application for iPhone right now, it cannot read messages, remote capturing.However, other functions (call sync, address book, pedometer, calendar, stopwatch, calculator, alarm function, music) works well.

2. Q:How to connect Bluetooth

A: First, download and install the APK in your Android devices (option)

Second, open Bluetooth on your devices and watch.

Third, you can use your devices to search the U8 watch, or use U8 watch to search the device you want to match. When searching finished, please connect them by following the notice.

3. Q: Does this watch work with the Galaxy S5

A: Yes, this Bluetooth Smart U Watch is compatible with all Bluetooth V2.0 Or above enabled smartphones (support Android 2.3 or above), such as iPhone 4, 4S, 5, 5S, Samsung S3, S4, Note 2, Note 3, Note 4 etc.

4. Q: Is it waterproof or water resistant

A: It is Normal waterproof; a little water is no problem. But never put it into water.

5. Q: Does the watch have internal earphone port to listen music

A: No, it doesn't have headphone jack, but it has its own speaker in it.

6. Q: Can you use this watch on Nokia windows phone

A: No. It is for Android Phone & iPhone only.

7. Q: Can you answer calls directly from the phone

A: yes, it supports phone answering. You also can dial through the watch.

8. Q: The music function of the watch only controls the music player or does the sound come through the watch speaker too

A: Yes, it controls the music player and also the sound comes through the watch speaker.

9. Q: When you are on the clock / watch mode, does the screen sleep Or do I need to keep pressing the power button to know the time of day

A: Yes, the screen will sleep. You need to press the power button to know the time.

Maybe you can set the LCD backlight time according to your requirements.

10. Q: Is this a watch smart phone or a blue tooth watch, and does it vibrates when I get a text message

A: It is a Bluetooth watch, can connect with your smart phone, and can make it vibrate when you get a text message. But only supports Android System. (Please install APK)

11. Q: Can this watch display a received text message for iPhone 5 I know it definitely cannot send message, but will it display And can it control music

A: It does not display text messages on iPhone, but you can control the music.

12. Q: Does it work for tablets too

A: No, it cannot!

13. Q: Can it be set to silently vibrate when you receive a call

A: Yes, you can set through Ringtone function.

14. Q: What is the battery life like on a day to day basis

A: Talk Time: about 3 hours

Music Play Time: about 6 hours

Standby Time: about 160 hours

Power Supply: Built-in 230mAh rechargeable battery

15. Q: Does it support images Can i see my photos on it

A: No, it doesn't support images.

name: Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones Headset
short_description:
Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones Headset
After extensive research, Bluedio has found that current headphones on the market have lots of common defects, such as serious noise, flat sound, stuffy appearance, etc. For these reasons, after 3 years of R&D, Bluedio have come up with the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset. 

The Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset is compatible with iOS, Android, and Windows.

Iconic powerful bass resonance
57mm ultra-large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, and Bluedio's iconic surging low-frequency shock let you feel deep bass resonance for superior sound quality.

Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1
With the robust high speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H boasts a long usage time of 40 hours of music, 45 hours talk time, and 1625 hours (approximately 67 days) standby time. Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction reduce ambient noise while speaking.

Customized function
Audio Sharing allows you to connect to another H headset via an audio cable, and share music with your friends (* it is recommended that headphones with impedance of 32 or higher be used). Simultaneously connect two Bluetooth devices, connect with your phone and tablet seamlessly, and  listen to music as you please!

Comfort
Custom fit supra-aural soft earmuffs and artificial protein leather of earmuffs simulated to human skin texture ensure long-lasting comfort.

Convenience
Just plug in with an audio cable (SOLD SEPARATELY), and listen to your favorite music tracks. The Hurricane H also has voice prompts in 4 languages (English, French, Spanish, and Chinese).

SPECIFICATIONS:
  • Drivers: 57mm speaker X 2
  • Transducer type: dynamic
  • Bluetooth version: V4.1
  • Frequency range: 2.4GHz-2.48GHz
  • Operating distance: up to 10m (free space)
  • Bluetooth profiles: A2DPAVRCPHSPHFP
  • Impedance: 16
  • Frequency response: 20Hz-20kHz
  • Sensitivity: 110dB
  • Distortion:<0.1%(THD)
  • Music playtime: up to 40 hours
  • Talk time: up to 45 hours
  • Standby time: up to 1625 hours
  • Charging time: about 2 hours
  • Operational temperature: -10 to 50°C

name: Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones Headset
short_description:
Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones HeadsetAfter extensive research, Bluedio has found that current headphones on the market have lots of common defects, such as serious noise, flat sound, stuffy appearance, etc. For these reasons, after 3 years of R&D, Bluedio have come up with the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset. 
The Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset is compatible with iOS, Android, and Windows.
Iconic powerful bass resonance57mm ultra-large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, and Bluedio's iconic surging low-frequency shock let you feel deep bass resonance for superior sound quality.
Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1With the robust high speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H boasts a long usage time of 40 hours of music, 45 hours talk time, and 1625 hours (approximately 67 days) standby time. Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction reduce ambient noise while speaking.
Customized functionAudio Sharing allows you to connect to another H headset via an audio cable, and share music with your friends (* it is recommended that headphones with impedance of 32 or higher be used). Simultaneously connect two Bluetooth devices, connect with your phone and tablet seamlessly, and  listen to music as you please!
ComfortCustom fit supra-aural soft earmuffs and artificial protein leather of earmuffs simulated to human skin texture ensure long-lasting comfort.
ConvenienceJust plug in with an audio cable (SOLD SEPARATELY), and listen to your favorite music tracks. The Hurricane H also has voice prompts in 4 languages (English, French, Spanish, and Chinese).
SPECIFICATIONS:
Drivers: 57mm speaker X 2
Transducer type: dynamic
Bluetooth version: V4.1
Frequency range: 2.4GHz-2.48GHz
Operating distance: up to 10m (free space)
Bluetooth profiles: A2DPAVRCPHSPHFP
Impedance: 16
Frequency response: 20Hz-20kHz
Sensitivity: 110dB
Distortion:
Music playtime: up to 40 hours
Talk time: up to 45 hours
Standby time: up to 1625 hours
Charging time: about 2 hours
Operational temperature: -10 to 50°C..

name: Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones Headset COLOR BLACK
short_description:
DESCRIPTION
Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones HeadsetAfter extensive research, Bluedio has found that current headphones on the market have lots of common defects, such as serious noise, flat sound, stuffy appearance, etc. 
For these reasons, after 3 years of R&D, Bluedio have come up with the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset.
  The Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset is compatible with iOS, Android, and Windows.
conic powerful bass resonance57mm ultra-large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, and Bluedio's iconic surging low-frequency shock let you feel deep bass resonance for superior sound quality. Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1With the robust high speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H boasts a long usage time of 40 hours of music, 45 hours talk time, and 1625 hours (approximately 67 days) standby time. Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction reduce ambient noise while speaking.
Customized functionAudio Sharing allows you to connect to another H headset via an audio cable, and share music with your friends (* it is recommended that headphones with impedance of 32 or higher be used). Simultaneously connect two Bluetooth devices, connect with your phone and tablet seamlessly, and  listen to music as you please!

  • Frequency range: 2.4GHz-2.48GHz
  • Operating distance: up to 10m (free space)
  • Bluetooth profiles: A2DPAVRCPHSPHFP
  • Impedance: 16

short_description:
Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones HeadsetAfter extensive research, Bluedio has found that current headphones on the market have lots of common defects, such as serious noise, flat sound, stuffy appearance, etc. For these reasons, after 3 years of R&D, Bluedio have come up with the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset. 

The Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset is compatible with iOS, Android, and Windows.
Iconic powerful bass resonance57mm ultra-large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, and Bluedio's iconic surging low-frequency shock let you feel deep bass resonance for superior sound quality

Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1With the robust high speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H boasts a long usage time of 40 hours of music, 45 hours talk time, and 1625 hours (approximately 67 days) standby time. Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction reduce ambient noise while speaking.

Customized functionAudio Sharing allows you to connect to another H headset via an audio cable, and share music with your friends (* it is recommended that headphones with impedance of 32 or higher be used). Simultaneously connect two Bluetooth devices, connect with your phone and tablet seamlessly, and  listen to music as you please

ComfortCustom fit supra-aural soft earmuffs and artificial protein leather of earmuffs simulated to human skin texture ensure long-lasting comfort.
ConvenienceJust plug in with an audio cable (SOLD SEPARATELY), and listen to your favorite music tracks. The Hurricane H also has voice prompts in 4 languages (English, French, Spanish, and Chinese).

  • Drivers: 57mm speaker X 2
  • Transducer type: dynamic
  • Bluetooth version: V4.1
  • Frequency range: 2.4GHz-2.48GHz
  • Operating distance: up to 10m (free space)
  • Bluetooth profiles: A2DPAVRCPHSPHFP
  • Impedance: 16
  • Frequency response: 20Hz-20kHz

name: U8 Bluetooth Smart Wrist Watch - White
short_description:
The U8 Bluetooth Smart Wrist Watch lets you stay in step with the time and the world in a new age way. This smart wrist watch features a high resolution, 1.48inch, capacitive touch display that enables you to see what matters at a glance. A high quality, white, plastic strap augments the watch’s matching white, stainless steel case further. The U8 smartwatch pairs with tablets, smartphones, and PCs that operate on Android v2.3 or higher. It is also compatible with iOS operating systems via its Bluetooth v2.0. It enables handsfree calls and gives you instant and discreet access to your mobile’s phonebook, notifications, and more. Those who have paired their Android smart devices with this accessory will also get notifications when they receive messages on WeChat, Twitter, Facebook, Skype, WhatsApp, and other such apps. Android users can also click pictures remotely with this smartwatch. An onboard passometer accurately counts the number of steps you take throughout the day. The timepiece incorporates an altitude meter, stopwatch, and barometer for your convenience.

Key Features

Bluetooth V3.0

Music Play Time: about 6 hours

Standby Time: about 160 hours

Talk Time: about 3 hours

230 mAh

Elegant, Durable Construction

This U8 watch is made using superior quality materials that look good and last long. Fine quality plastic is used in the making of its white band, which holds a matching, stainless steel case and wraps comfortably around your wrists. Atop the case is the watch’s 1.48inch, capacitive touch display that produces incredible visuals and provides at a glance information.

Multiple Functionality

This U8 smartwatch provides a ringing reminder whenever you receive a call or when your phone is disconnected from this accessory. The accessory’s anti lost alarm function can be programmed to set off automatically whenever your phone is out of its 10m transmitting range. It even displays the caller ID of the person calling you.

name: Bluedio Foldable Turbine T2 Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones Headset Black
short_description:
Iconic powerful bass resonance:
57mm ultra-large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, and Bluedio's iconic surging low-frequency shock let you feel deep bass resonance for superior sound quality.

Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1
With the robust high speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H boasts a long usage time of 40 hours of music, 45 hours talk time, and 1625 hours (approximately 67 days) standby time. 
Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction reduce ambient noise while speaking.

Customized function:
Audio Sharing allows you to connect to another H headset via an audio cable, and share music with your friends (* it is recommended that headphones with impedance of 32 or higher be used). Simultaneously connect two Bluetooth devices, connect with your phone and tablet seamlessly, and listen to music as you please!

Comfort:
Custom fit supra-aural soft earmuffs and artificial protein leather of earmuffs simulated to human skin texture ensure long-lasting comfort.

Convenience:
Just plug in with an audio cable , and listen to your favorite music tracks. The Hurricane H also has voice prompts in 4 languages (English, French, Spanish, and Chinese).

name: U8 Bluetooth Smart Watch Samsung S3/S4/S5/Note 2/3/4, Android Smart phones
short_description:
Bluetooth Smart U Watch which is compatible with all Bluetooth V2.0 or above enabled smartphones, tablets and PCs (support Android 2.3 or above),such as Samsung S3, S4, Note 2, Note 3, Note 4 etc.

Features:

  • 1.48" Capacitive Touch Screen TFT LCD
  • Time / Date / Battery state display
  • Ringing reminder when you receive a call
  • Ringing reminder once your mobile phone disconnected
  • Display the number or name of incoming calls
  • Answer or Dial calls from your wrist
  • Stopwatch function
  • Support hands-free calls, phone book
  • Play the music in your phone (after Bluetooth paring)
  • Sync SMS/call history
  • Ring reminder when your Android 2.3 or above smart phone receive a message (including  Facebook, Twitter, WhatsApp, Skype, and so on)
  • Anti-lost alarm function: When cellphone left watch alarm automatically, after a certain distance to avoid lose the phones
  • Remote taking photo function: You can control your cellphone to take photo from your wrist.
  • Altitude Meter, Pedometer
  • Atmosphere temperature and pressure

Specifications:

  • Material: Plastic Silicon
  • Language Support: English, French, Spanish, Portuguese, Korean, Italian, German, Turkish, Russian, Japanese, Chinese
  • Charging Time: about 1 hour
  • Talk Time: about 3 hours
  • Music Play Time: about 6 hours
  • Standby Time: about 160 hours
  • Power Supply: Built-in 230 mAh rechargeable battery

Package includes:

1 x Bluetooth Watch

1 x USB cable

1 x Charger

1 x User Manual

 

To enjoy the full features of your smartwatch, you must download and install the program "Mediatek Smart Device" from the Google play store on your android phone.

 


  • bluetooth smartwatch
  • pairs with your android phone
  • answer and dial calls from your watch
  • read sms messgaes on your watch
  • get alerts of any new notification on your phone

name: Bluedio Q5 Sport Bluetooth Headset - Green
short_description:
The Bluedio Q5 Sport Bluetooth Headset lets you enjoy hours of high quality music from any compatible audio device such as your smartphone or portable audio player. These headsets give you the perfect balance of comfort, style, and amazing audio quality. It sports an eye catchy green color that looks very trendy once you wear it. It is compact and portable, which makes it easy to use or carry anywhere. Bluetooth v4.1 chip enables wireless listening of songs when on the move. Similarly, the high quality built in battery ensures long hours of music playback. You can enjoy handsfree calls via the microphone. This Bluetooth music headset is compatible with various Bluetooth enabled devices.

Key Features

Bluetooth

Micro USB

Lightweight, Ergonomic Fit

The Bluedio wireless headset is designed to provide a comfortable feel and is engineered to deliver an incredible listening experience. Its in ear form factor gives you the ultimate comfort and fit. The headset is made out of sturdy materials that are strong enough to withstand daily use. It sports a lightweight design that offers complete ease and comfort for prolonged usage.

Wireless Listening

Equipped with high end features like Bluetooth 4.1 chip, microphone, high quality battery, it's no wonder that the Bluedio Q5 Sport reviews are so favorable. This wireless headset can be charged via a USB cable. It offers a standby time of 220 hours when charged fully. The headset makes for a perfect workout companion, as it leaves behind all dongles and wires that tend to be troublesome. You can also answer calls via this headset as it has a microphone built in.

name: Bluedio Q5 Wireless Bluetooth Sport Stereo Headset - Blue
short_description:
The Bluedio Wireless 4.1 Bluetooth Anti Sweat Sport Stereo Headset provides an immersive audio experience. Thanks to an innovative noise cancellation feature, you can now enjoy listening to your favorite soundtracks even in crowded areas. This function eliminates all the ambient sounds, and only the music you are listening to is focused upon. The earbuds of this headset are soft and fit in your ears comfortably. The earphones are fully compatible with devices running Android, IOS, and Windows operating systems. It features Bluetooth v4.1 that allows you to enjoy music wirelessly. This headset sports a trendy blue finish that enhances its overall appeal.

Key Features

20Hz-20KHz

Talking Time :7 hours

Charge Time : 1-2 hours

16ohm

Music Time: 6 hours

Trendy Looks

The Bluedio Wireless 4.1 Bluetooth Anti Sweat Sport Stereo Headset is lightweight and compact in size that enhances its portability. It is stylish to look at and appears chic in a sleek blue finish. The earphones feature an ergonomic design and fit comfortably in your ears.

Smart and Efficient

The Bluedio Wireless 4.1 Bluetooth Anti Sweat Sport Stereo Headset incorporates the Bluetooth v4.1 technology that strengthens the performance of data transmission and gives you a smooth operating experience. You can download Smart APP on your smartphone to control the earphones and adjust the volume directly from your device. This app is compatible with Android v4.0 or above. The earphones also include a new feature called HD calls that allows you to enjoy wireless HD calls. An advanced sixth generation CVC noise reduction technology has been incorporated into the earphones that blocks out unwanted sounds and distortion to allow you to focus on your music completely.

Advanced Functionality

The Bluedio Wireless 4.1 Bluetooth Anti Sweat Sport Stereo Headset is designed to be moisture proof and sweat resistant. Thus, you can wear this headset while jogging or working out at a gym without worrying about it getting damaged. The earphones feature voice prompts in four languages that include English, Chinese, French, and Spanish. You can select the one as per your requirement by clicking the multifunction button and volume.

ICONIC POWERFUL BASS RESONANCE:
57MM ULTRA-LARGE DYNAMIC DRIVERS, TURBINE STYLE HOUSING, AND BLUEDIO'S ICONIC SURGING LOW-FREQUENCY SHOCK LET YOU FEEL DEEP BASS RESONANCE FOR SUPERIOR SOUND QUALITY.

ULTRA-LONG OPERATION AND CAREFREE CALLING FROM BLUETOOTH 4.1

ACOUSTIC ECHO CANCELLATION AND NOISE REDUCTION REDUCE AMBIENT NOISE WHILE SPEAKING.

AUDIO SHARING ALLOWS YOU TO CONNECT TO ANOTHER H HEADSET VIA AN AUDIO CABLE, AND SHARE MUSIC WITH YOUR FRIENDS (* IT IS RECOMMENDED THAT HEADPHONES WITH IMPEDANCE OF 32 OR HIGHER BE USED). COMFORT:
CUSTOM FIT SUPRA-AURAL SOFT EARMUFFS AND ARTIFICIAL PROTEIN LEATHER OF EARMUFFS SIMULATED TO HUMAN SKIN TEXTURE ENSURE LONG-LASTING COMFORT.

JUST PLUG IN WITH AN AUDIO CABLE , AND LISTEN TO YOUR FAVORITE MUSIC TRACKS. THE HURRICANE H ALSO HAS VOICE PROMPTS IN 4 LANGUAGES (ENGLISH, FRENCH, SPANISH, AND CHINESE).

name: Bluedio T2 Dynamic Wireless Bluetooth Headphones - Black
short_description:
Have a good music listening experience with the Bluedio T2 Dynamic Wireless Bluetooth Headphones that are equipped with high end technologies. The headphones support Bluetooth 4.1 and boast a long usage time. They offer 40 hours of music playback, 45 hours of talk time, and 1625 hours of standby time. The 57mm ultra large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, and iconic surging low frequency shock technology work together to deliver deep bass resonance for excellent music quality. These headphones also facilitate handsfree calling as they feature a built in microphone and can connect to your smartphone wirelessly. This pair of headphones also looks incredibly good thanks to their unique design and a stunning black finish.

Key Features

Bluetooth

536 g

Micro USB

Trendy Appearance

The Bluetooth music headset is designed keeping in mind today’s fashion forward generation. It takes on a quirky yet elegant look that gels well with any attire. In addition, this Bluetooth headset has a compact and lightweight structure for easy carrying and storage. Along with a good look, this headset offers complete comfort via its on the ear earcups that provide a comfortable feel.

Great Sound Quality

This high quality Bluetooth headset has been engineered after thorough research. It incorporates 57mm ultra large dynamic drivers with turbine style housing and Bluedio’s iconic surging low frequency shock. They together deliver deep bass resonance, clear highs, and deep lows, for a superior sound quality.

Functional and Practical

The Bluedio T2 Dynamic headset is integrated with the amazing Bluetooth 4.1 chip that works perfectly with your smartphone, tablet or Bluetooth enabled MP3 players. This headset boasts a long usage duration; it offers 40 hours of music playback, 45 hours of talk time, and 1625 hours of standby time. Plus, its echo cancelation and noise reduction capability ensure a crystal clear calling and listening experience.

name: Bluedio N2 Sports Wireless Bluetooth Stereo Earbuds Headset - Black
short_description:
The Bluedio N2 Sports Wireless Bluetooth Stereo Earbuds Headset is the perfect companion for your training sessions. Multiple studies conclude that listening to music helps you work out harder and improves your endurance, but the problem is finding a headset that stays in place while you work out. The Black N2 Sports Headset features an ergonomic design with comfortable ear tips that stay secured to your ears while you move. It features a unique cow horn design to ensure a snug fit and optimal comfort. The headset features Bluetooth 4.1 technology and can pair with any Bluetooth enabled device from up to 10m away.

Key Features

Sweat and moisture-proof

Reproduced true sound

6th generation CVC noise reduction

Buttons YES or NO

Bluetooth 4.1 Connectivity

The Bluedio N2 Wireless Headset features Bluetooth 4.1 technology to pair with your smartphone. Bluetooth and 4G LTE signals often interfere with each other and degrade one another’s performance and drain battery life quickly. Bluetooth 4.1 manages both signals automatically, so there’s no overlap and battery life is not hampered. The Bluedio N2 Wireless Headset with Bluetooth 4.1 is future proof and is a perfect complement to your 4G LTE handset.

Passive Noise Cancellation for Immersive Sound

The Bluedio N2 Bluetooth Headset features 6th generation CVC noise reduction technology. It significantly improves and alters the spectral shape of the receive path signal by using sophisticated algorithms. It removes unwanted noise and improves far end voice frequencies for crystal clear audio during a handsfree conversation.

Superior Sound

The Bluedio Bluetooth Stereo Headset is crafted with 10mm dynamic drivers and features a CCAW voice coil. The headset delivers a full bodied timber with clear, bright, and better transient response to reproduce the actual sound of your favorite tunes.

Ergonomic Sweat Proof Design

The Bluedio N2 Wireless Headset features compact and light earbuds that ensure comfortable wear and minimum listener fatigue. Silicone ear tips provide added comfort and also deliver excellent sweat and water resistance.

name: White Color Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones Headset
short_description:
Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones Headset After extensive research, Bluedio has found that current headphones on the market have lots of common defects, such as serious noise, flat sound, stuffy appearance, etc. For these reasons, after 3 years of R&D, Bluedio have come up with the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset.
The Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset is compatible with iOS, Android, and Windows.
Iconic powerful bass resonance57mm ultra-large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, and Bluedio's iconic surging low-frequency shock let you feel deep bass resonance for superior sound quality.

Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1 With the robust high speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H boasts a long usage time of 40 hours of music, 45 hours talk time, and 1625 hours (approximately 67 days) standby time. Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction reduce ambient noise while speaking.

Customized functionAudio Sharing allows you to connect to another H headset via an audio cable, and share music with your friends (* it is recommended that headphones with impedance of 32 or higher be used). Simultaneously connect two Bluetooth devices, connect with your phone and tablet seamlessly, and listen to music as you please!
ComfortCustom fit supra-aural soft earmuffs and artificial protein leather of earmuffs simulated to human skin texture ensure long-lasting comfort.
ConvenienceJust plug in with an audio cable (SOLD SEPARATELY), and listen to your favorite music tracks. The Hurricane H also has voice prompts in 4 languages (English, French, Spanish, and Chinese).

name: U8 Silicone Aluminum Bluetooth Smart Watch - Black
short_description:
U8 Bluetooth smart watch is a must have for busy individuals and sports enthusiasts. This U8 smart watch has a 1.48inch touch screen.The U8 Silicone Aluminum Bluetooth Smart Watch brings the functions of a smartphone on your wrist. Just connect your Android, iOS mobiles with the watch and access all their features in a better, smarter way. It has Bluetooth 3.0 technology that lets you make the connection quickly wirelessly. It has a 1.48inch touch screen that responds ultra quickly and displays everything clearly. When you are working, you don’t have the time to look at your phone for notifications, time, etc. The watch attached to your wrist is then the best and quick way to answer or reject calls, see all notifications, and access various features with simple touch gestures.

Key Features

1.48 Inch

230mAh

Compatible with IOS, Android and Windows

Do It the Smart Way

This U8 smart watch is compatible with Apple iPhone, Samsung S2, S3, S4, Note 2, Note 3, HTC, and Sony smartphones. Connect your devices with the watch using its Bluetooth 3.0 technology. With simple gestures, you can answer or reject calls, read messages, control music playback, and even take photos remotely. You can set up to five alarms daily on the watch. This U8 black smartwatch can also be used as a stopwatch, barometer, and passometer when performing a sports activity.

Intuitive Interface and Ergonomic Make

This U8 Bluetooth smart watch features a 1.48inch, capacitive TFT LCD that displays everything in clear and bright picture quality. It has built in 230mAh rechargeable battery provides up to three hours of talk time, six hours of music playback time, and160 hours of standby time. Its band is made using silicone to make it soft, flexible, and durable.

name: Bluedio Turbine T2 Bluetooth Stereo Headphones - Blue
short_description:
The blue colored Bluedio Turbine T2 Bluetooth Stereo Headphones will change the way you listen to music. They are designed to deliver accurate, loud, and detailed audio, and also suit everyday listening via compatible devices. The headphones incorporate high quality 57mm ultra large dynamic drivers, a turbine style housing, and the iconic surging low frequency shock technology that lets you feel deep bass resonance for a richer listening experience. Its Bluetooth 4.1 chip enables wireless music listening while the built in battery offers prolonged hours of music playback. Apart from providing excellent audio quality, these headphones from Bluedio also offer complete comfort with their soft and comfy earcups. The Bluedio Turbine T2 Bluetooth Stereo Headphones have a compact and lightweight form factor that lets you place or store them securely.

Key Features

Bluetooth

536 g

Micro USB

Trendy Appearance

The Bluetooth music headset is designed keeping in mind today’s fashion forward generation. It takes on a quirky yet elegant look that gels well with any attire. In addition, this Bluetooth headset has a compact and lightweight structure for easy carrying and storage. Along with a good look, this headset offers complete comfort via its on the ear earcups that provide a comfortable feel.

Great Sound Quality

This high quality Bluetooth headset has been engineered after thorough research. It incorporates 57mm ultra large dynamic drivers with turbine style housing and Bluedio’s iconic surging low frequency shock. They together deliver deep bass resonance, clear highs, and deep lows, for a superior sound quality.

Functional and Practical

The Bluedio T2 Dynamic headset is integrated with the amazing Bluetooth 4.1 chip that works perfectly with your smartphone, tablet or Bluetooth enabled MP3 players. This headset boasts a long usage duration; it offers 40 hours of music playback, 45 hours of talk time, and 1625 hours of standby time. Plus, its echo cancelation and noise reduction capability ensure a crystal clear calling and listening experience.

name: Bluedio HT(Shooting Brake) Wireless Bluetooth 4.1 Stereo Headphone Headset
short_description:
Features:
Iconic powerful bass resonance of Bluedio:
Unexpected
57mm ultra-large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, with iconic
Bluedio surging low-frequency shock, let you feel the bass resonate deep
in the chest, enjoying the best sound quality. Clear and transparent
bass, mids and highs, fully exposed to all the details of song, you can
hear what the artists really want you to hear, Coldplay or Linkin Park
concerts are simply playing around your ear.
Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1:


With robust high speed CPU of
Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, comes with ultra-long 40 hours music, 45
hours talk and 1625 hours (around 67 days) standby time, the same
battery, decrease up to 40% power consumption compare to Bluetooth 4.0.
Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction effectively reduce
ambient noise while talking, make far-end listener cannot hear what you
said become history, just like talking face to face.
Customized function:
Audio
Sharing allows you to connect to another H(Shooting Brake) headphone
via audio cable, share music feast with your friends
instantly(*recommended to use headphones with impedance of 32 or
higher). Seamless connect two Bluetooth devices simultaneously, listen
to music or enjoy foreign blockbusters, do as you think about it.
Comfortable wearing:
Custom
fit supra-aural soft earmuffs, artificial protein leather of earmuffs
simulated to human skin texture, ensure long lasting comfort in various
rugged circumstances.
Convenience:
Just
a plug with audio cable(*buy separately), then listen to your favorite
tracks without using any battery, no matter how long is your playlist.
H-turbine also incorporate 4 languages voice prompt(Chinese, English,
French, Spanish), to communicate with you in your language

Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1:
With
robust high speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, comes with
ultra-long 40 hours music, 45 hours talk and 1625 hours (around 67 days)
standby time, the same battery, decrease up to 40% power consumption
compare to Bluetooth 4.0. Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction
effectively reduce ambient noise while talking, make far-end listener
cannot hear what you said become history, just like talking face to
face.



Customized function:
Audio Sharing allows
you to connect to another H headphone via audio cable, share music
feast with your friends instantly(*recommended to use headphones with
impedance
of 32 or higher). Seamless connect two Bluetooth devices
simultaneously, listen to music or enjoy foreign blockbusters, do as you
think about it.



Comfortable wearing:

soft earmuffs, artificial protein leather of earmuffs simulated to human
skin texture, ensure long lasting comfort in various rugged
circumstances.



Convenience:
Just a plug with audio
cable(*buy separately), then listen to your favorite tracks without
using any battery, no matter how long is your playlist. H-turbine also
incorporate 4 languages voice prompt(Chinese, English, French, Spanish),
to communicate with you in your language.

Ongoing luxurious Bluetooth 4.1 Headphone, delighting the world.

Luxurious music enjoyment is always unreachable. For this reason,
Bluedio keep hard working on 3 years of R&D and testing, manage to
customize a wireless headphone with unrivaled timbre, adapted to a
variety of rugged circumstances and highly cost- effective. Thoughtful
design, unexpected superior sound, make luxury become reasonable, this
is Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 headphone. Thus, H is compatible with
iOS, Android, and Windows, merely 40ms audio latency breakthrough
defects of sound and picture are not synchronized while watching movie
via Bluetooth. It also work as a BT receiver connecting mobile phone and
professional amplifier wirelessly. Insert Micro-SD card which saved
with music files into the headphone SD card slot. Remove Micro-SD card
under Micro-SD card mode, headset will change to FM mode. Insert
Micro-SD card under FM mode, headset will change to Micro-SD card mode.
But it may affect function of the headset,
do not suggest the above usage.

name: Bluedio N2 Sports Wireless Bluetooth Stereo Earbuds Headset - White
short_description:
The Bluedio N2 Sports Wireless Bluetooth Stereo Earbuds Headset provides a comfortable and pleasant listening experience due to its ergonomic design. With a specially designed T Light 3 Cow Horn Ear Cup, the headset provides a snug fit and ultimate comfort. The ear cups are made from high quality silicone and are well sealed to ensure optimal noise cancellation. Furthermore, with 6th generation CVC Denoise Technology, this white headset eliminates outside noise to provide an immersive listening experience. This handsfree headset also allows you to pick up or reject calls with voice commands.

Key Features

Sweat and moisture-proof

Reproduced true sound

6th generation CVC noise reduction

Buttons YES or NO

Bluetooth 4.1 Connectivity

The Bluedio N2 Wireless Headset features Bluetooth 4.1 technology to pair with your smartphone. Bluetooth and 4G LTE signals often interfere with each other and degrade one another’s performance and drain battery life quickly. Bluetooth 4.1 manages both signals automatically, so there’s no overlap and battery life is not hampered. The Bluedio N2 Wireless Headset with Bluetooth 4.1 is future proof and is a perfect complement to your 4G LTE handset.

Passive Noise Cancellation for Immersive Sound

The Bluedio N2 Bluetooth Headset features 6th generation CVC noise reduction technology. It significantly improves and alters the spectral shape of the receive path signal by using sophisticated algorithms. It removes unwanted noise and improves far end voice frequencies for crystal clear audio during a handsfree conversation.

Superior Sound

The Bluedio Bluetooth Stereo Headset is crafted with 10mm dynamic drivers and features a CCAW voice coil. The headset delivers a full bodied timber with clear, bright, and better transient response to reproduce the actual sound of your favorite tunes.

Ergonomic Sweat Proof Design

The Bluedio N2 Wireless Headset features compact and light earbuds that ensure comfortable wear and minimum listener fatigue. Silicone ear tips provide added comfort and also deliver excellent sweat and water resistance.

name: Bluedio Turbine Hurricane HT Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones Headset
short_description:
The black colored Bluedio Turbine Hurricane HT Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones are one of a kind. They were made to please demanding users looking for a wireless headset with great audio technologies. The HT Headphones comes with several high tech features found in today’s high end headsets, and are without a doubt one of the best wireless, high tech headsets. They diminish the need for cables and make listening to songs a clutter free experience. With regards to the audio performance, the HT headset is quite magnificent. Its technology is based on 57mm ultra large dynamic drivers that deliver a well balanced sound, with clear bass, and incredible treble, which together allow you to listen to the tiniest details of a song. The noise cancelation and noise reduction features efficiently reduce ambient noise while talking or listening to music. As far as convenience is concerned, the headset features custom fit, supra aural, soft earmuffs made of artificial protein leather to ensure long lasting comfort. The language prompt on the HT headset comes ready with 4 languages, English, Spanish, French, and English, to make communicating easy.

Physical Features

Key Features

Bluetooth V4.1

209.8 g

16 ohms

Powerful Bass

The Bluedio Turbine Hurricane HT Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones deliver a strong bass thanks to its great 57mm ultra large dynamic drivers. It offers surging, low frequency shock to let you feel a deep, resonating bass. Whether it's Linkin Park or Maroon 5, you get clear and transparent bass, precise mids, and highs, and every single detail in the way the artist intended it to be heard.

Ultra Long Operation

The Bluedio Turbine Hurricane HT Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones have a Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, which offers ultra long usage of 40 hours of music playback, 45 hours of talk time, and 1625 hours of standby time. This technology also reduces power consumption by up to 40 percent as compared to the previous Bluetooth 4.0 fidelity.

Customized Function

The Bluedio Turbine Hurricane HT Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones offer a fully customized service that allows you to connect to another HT headphone via an audio cable, and share songs with buddies. You can also connect two Bluetooth devices at the same time.

name: Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones Headset white color
short_description:
BLUEDIO TURBINE HURRICANE H BLUETOOTH 4.1 WIRELESS STEREO HEADPHONES HEADSET AFTER EXTENSIVE RESEARCH, BLUEDIO HAS FOUND THAT CURRENT HEADPHONES ON THE MARKET HAVE LOTS OF COMMON DEFECTS, SUCH AS SERIOUS NOISE, FLAT SOUND, STUFFY APPEARANCE, ETC. FOR THESE REASONS, AFTER 3 YEARS OF R&D, BLUEDIO HAVE COME UP WITH THE BLUEDIO TURBINE HURRICANE H HEADSET.
THE BLUEDIO TURBINE HURRICANE H HEADSET IS COMPATIBLE WITH IOS, ANDROID, AND WINDOWS
ICONIC POWERFUL BASS RESONANCE57MM ULTRA-LARGE DYNAMIC DRIVERS, TURBINE STYLE HOUSING, AND BLUEDIO'S ICONIC SURGING LOW-FREQUENCY SHOCK LET YOU FEEL DEEP BASS RESONANCE FOR SUPERIOR SOUND QUALITY.
ULTRA-LONG OPERATION AND CAREFREE CALLING FROM BLUETOOTH 4.1 WITH THE ROBUST HIGH SPEED CPU OF BLUETOOTH 4.1 OPERATING SYSTEM, THE BLUEDIO TURBINE HURRICANE H BOASTS A LONG USAGE TIME OF 40 HOURS OF MUSIC, 45 HOURS TALK TIME, AND 1625 HOURS (APPROXIMATELY 67 DAYS) STANDBY TIME. ACOUSTIC ECHO CANCELLATION AND NOISE REDUCTION REDUCE AMBIENT NOISE WHILE SPEAKING.

CUSTOMIZED FUNCTIONAUDIO SHARING ALLOWS YOU TO CONNECT TO ANOTHER H HEADSET VIA AN AUDIO CABLE, AND SHARE MUSIC WITH YOUR FRIENDS (* IT IS RECOMMENDED THAT HEADPHONES WITH IMPEDANCE OF 32 OR HIGHER BE USED). SIMULTANEOUSLY CONNECT TWO BLUETOOTH DEVICES, CONNECT WITH YOUR PHONE AND TABLET SEAMLESSLY, AND LISTEN TO MUSIC AS YOU PLEASE!

COMFORTCUSTOM FIT SUPRA-AURAL SOFT EARMUFFS AND ARTIFICIAL PROTEIN LEATHER OF EARMUFFS SIMULATED TO HUMAN SKIN TEXTURE ENSURE LONG-LASTING COMFORT.

CONVENIENCEJUST PLUG IN WITH AN AUDIO CABLE (SOLD SEPARATELY), AND LISTEN TO YOUR FAVORITE MUSIC TRACKS. THE HURRICANE H ALSO HAS VOICE PROMPTS IN 4 LANGUAGES (ENGLISH, FRENCH, SPANISH, AND CHINESE).

SPECIFICATIONS:
  • Drivers: 57mm speaker X 2
  • Transducer type: dynamic
  • Bluetooth version: V4.1
  • Frequency range: 2.4GHz-2.48GHz
  • Operating distance: up to 10m (free space)
  • Bluetooth profiles: A2DPAVRCPHSPHFP
  • Impedance: 16
  • Frequency response: 20Hz-20kHz
  • Sensitivity: 110dB
  • Distortion:

name: Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones Headset black
short_description:
Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo
Headphones Headset After extensive research, Bluedio has found that
current headphones on the market have lots of common defects, such as
serious noise, flat sound, stuffy appearance, etc. For these reasons,
after 3 years of R&D, Bluedio have come up with the Bluedio Turbine
Hurricane H Headset.

The Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset is compatible with iOS, Android, and Windows.
Iconic powerful bass resonance57mm
ultra-large dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, and Bluedio's
iconic surging low-frequency shock let you feel deep bass resonance for
superior sound quality.
Ultra-long
operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1 With the robust high
speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, the Bluedio Turbine
Hurricane H boasts a long usage time of 40 hours of music, 45 hours talk
time, and 1625 hours (approximately 67 days) standby time. Acoustic
echo cancellation and noise reduction reduce ambient noise while
speaking.

Customized functionAudio
Sharing allows you to connect to another H headset via an audio cable,
and share music with your friends (* it is recommended that headphones
with impedance of 32 or higher be used). Simultaneously connect two
Bluetooth devices, connect with your phone and tablet seamlessly, and
listen to music as you please!
ComfortCustom
fit supra-aural soft earmuffs and artificial protein leather of
earmuffs simulated to human skin texture ensure long-lasting comfort.
ConvenienceJust plug in with an audio cable (SOLD SEPARATELY),
and listen to your favorite music tracks. The Hurricane H also has
voice prompts in 4 languages (English, French, Spanish, and Chinese).

name: Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones Headset PC SmartPHone Samsung
short_description:
Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless Stereo Headphones HeadsetAfter
extensive research, Bluedio has found that current headphones on the
market have lots of common defects, such as serious noise, flat sound,
stuffy appearance, etc. For these reasons, after 3 years of R&D,
Bluedio have come up with the Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset. 
The Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Headset is compatible with iOS, Android, and Windows.
Iconic powerful bass resonance57mm
ultra-large
dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, and Bluedio's iconic surging
low-frequency shock let you feel deep bass resonance for superior sound
quality.
Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth 4.1With
the robust high speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, the
Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H boasts a long usage time of 40 hours of
music, 45 hours talk time, and 1625 hours
(approximately 67 days) standby time. Acoustic echo
cancellation and noise reduction reduce ambient noise while
speaking.
Customized functionAudio
Sharing
allows you to connect to another H headset via an audio
cable, and share music with your friends (* it is recommended that
headphones with impedance of 32 or higher be used). Simultaneously
connect two
Bluetooth devices, connect with your phone and tablet seamlessly, and
 listen to music as you please!
ComfortCustom
fit supra-aural soft earmuffs and artificial protein leather of earmuffs
simulated to human skin texture ensure long-lasting comfort.
ConvenienceJust plug in with an audio cable (SOLD SEPARATELY),
and listen to your favorite music tracks. The Hurricane H also has
voice prompts in 4 languages (English, French, Spanish, and Chinese).
SPECIFICATIONS:

  • Drivers: 57mm speaker X 2
  • Transducer type: dynamic
  • Bluetooth version: V4.1
  • Frequency range: 2.4GHz-2.48GHz
  • Operating distance: up to 10m (free space)
  • Bluetooth profiles: A2DPAVRCPHSPHFP
  • Impedance: 16
  • Frequency response: 20Hz-20kHz
  • Sensitivity: 110dB
  • Distortion:
  • Music playtime: up to 40 hours
  • Talk time: up to 45 hours
  • Standby time: up to 1625 hours
  • Charging time: about 2 hours
  • Operational temperature: -10 to 50°C

name: DZ09 Bluetooth Smart Watch Single SIM Phone with Dialer Camera Sleep Monitor
short_description:
The smartwatches seem to keep coming from China as we now see the DZ09 listed on Gearbest for 
just $39,43. It’s a ‘watch phone’ which means you can insert a sim card 
into the little device and make and receive calls with it. There is 
also space for a micro-SD card to give it some extra storage. The 
display is a 1.56” inch display with a 240×240 resolution. The watch 
supports 2G GSM frequencies and comes with Bluetooth 3.0 which isn’t as 
energy efficient as Bluetooth 4.0 would have been. On the other hand, 
you don’t have to connect this watch to your smartphone because it practically is one. 
The watch also comes with 128MB RAM memory and 64MB internal storage, a 
533MHz Mediatek MT6260A processor and a 0.3 megapixel camera. Don’t 
expect too much from a camera like that, because it’s usually not very 
good at shooting good pictures. But it is a nice spy cam for that 
matter. The watch comes with a lot of features that we have seen more in 
the past few watches that have come by. It can play music, count steps, 
alert you when you are sedentary for too long and it can even monitor 
your sleep. And with the 380mAh battery the company says that you should 
be able to keep the device in standby for at least 180 hours. To be 
honest That sounds a bit much for a watch like this, and it wouldn’t be 
the first time that listed standby hours aren’t met in real life.

name: Solar Power Bank 8000 mAh
short_description:
Features:
  • Easily fits into your bag to provide instant power.
  • Anti-skid protecting design.
  • 1A output allows for simultaneous charging of your devices at high speed Anti-explosion, lightweight, compact and reliable
  • 1000 recharge cycles over the life of the battery.
  • Grade 5 Waterproof design ensures the device functions smoothly when it's raining.
  • Shock-proof feature ensures the device working properly in case of crashes or drops.
  • It adopts intelligent chip, support overcharge / discharge / overload and short circuit protection.
  • It can be fully charged under direct strong sunlight 
  • When you are in travel, it could be hanged on your backpack to absorb the sun light for charging.
  • LED charging indicators and a torch light for emergency.

Specifications:
  • Li-polymer battery: 8000mAh
  • Solar charging: 5V/200mA
  • Input: DC 5V/1A
  • Output: DC 5V/1A
  • Size:132 x 74 x 16mm
  • Weight: 150 g
  • Available Colors: Green / Blue
Package Contents:
  • Solar Power Bank
  • Hook
  • Micro USB cable
Attention!!
  • The actual capacity of the power bank is 8000 mAh, however, charging an already running devices will consume some of the charging power and the capacity might seem less than what is advertised. 
  • Solar energy technology is still under development, and charging the power bank through solar capability might take longer than what is expected.
  • This device is designed to handle a good amount of heat, however, it is not recommended to leave the device in the car or any closed areas for a long time where no ventilation is available. Overheating the internal circuit of this device or its solar cells might cause a permanent damage.
  • The expected amount of hours of a direct sun light in order to fully(0) charge the battery is 40 hours.

name: Bluedio T2 Dynamic Bluetooth Headset - Red
short_description:
The Bluedio T2 Dynamic Bluetooth Headset has been created after extensive research to deliver enhanced sound from its 57mm ultra large dynamic drivers. Its turbine style housing and Bluedio’s iconic surging low frequency shock let you feel deep bass for an unmatched sound quality. This red colored headset offers ultra long operation and handsfree calling via Bluetooth 4.1. It provides echo canceling and noise reduction while you speak, for a crystal clear calling experience.

Key Features

Bluetooth

536 g

Micro USB

Trendy Appearance

The Bluetooth music headset is designed keeping in mind today’s fashion forward generation. It takes on a quirky yet elegant look that gels well with any attire. In addition, this Bluetooth headset has a compact and lightweight structure for easy carrying and storage. Along with a good look, this headset offers complete comfort via its on the ear earcups that provide a comfortable feel.

Great Sound Quality

This high quality Bluetooth headset has been engineered after thorough research. It incorporates 57mm ultra large dynamic drivers with turbine style housing and Bluedio’s iconic surging low frequency shock. They together deliver deep bass resonance, clear highs, and deep lows, for a superior sound quality.

Functional and Practical

The Bluedio T2 Dynamic headset is integrated with the amazing Bluetooth 4.1 chip that works perfectly with your smartphone, tablet or Bluetooth enabled MP3 players. This headset boasts a long usage duration; it offers 40 hours of music playback, 45 hours of talk time, and 1625 hours of standby time. Plus, its echo cancelation and noise reduction capability ensure a crystal clear calling and listening experience.

short_description:
BLUEDIO TURBINE HURRICANE H BLUETOOTH 4.1 WIRELESS STEREO HEADPHONES HEADSETAFTER EXTENSIVE RESEARCH, BLUEDIO HAS FOUND THAT CURRENT HEADPHONES ON THE MARKET HAVE LOTS OF COMMON DEFECTS, SUCH AS SERIOUS NOISE, FLAT SOUND, STUFFY APPEARANCE, ETC.FOR THESE REASONS, AFTER 3 YEARS OF R&D, BLUEDIO HAVE COME UP WITH THE BLUEDIO TURBINE HURRICANE H HEADSET.  THE BLUEDIO TURBINE HURRICANE H HEADSET IS COMPATIBLE WITH IOS, ANDROID, AND WINDOWS.CONIC POWERFUL BASS RESONANCE57MM ULTRA-LARGE DYNAMIC DRIVERS, TURBINE STYLE HOUSING, AND BLUEDIO'S ICONIC SURGING LOW-FREQUENCY SHOCK LET YOU FEEL DEEP BASS RESONANCE FOR SUPERIOR SOUND QUALITY. ULTRA-LONG OPERATION AND CAREFREE CALLING FROM BLUETOOTH 4.1WITH THE ROBUST HIGH SPEED CPU OF BLUETOOTH 4.1 OPERATING SYSTEM, THE BLUEDIO TURBINE HURRICANE H BOASTS A LONG USAGE TIME OF 40 HOURS OF MUSIC, 45 HOURS TALK TIME, AND 1625 HOURS (APPROXIMATELY 67 DAYS) STANDBY TIME. ACOUSTIC ECHO CANCELLATION AND NOISE REDUCTION REDUCE AMBIENT NOISE WHILE SPEAKING.

short_description:
• The Lazy Bracket is the perfect accessory with which to watch movies, listen to music and play games, without having to hold your mobile device.
  • A heavy duty and sturdy holder, it holds your device securely in place and prevents the unit from moving around or falling.
  • Coupled with an extra long flexible goose-neck a 360 degree rotating clasp, positioning your device with one hand is extremely easy, whether in landscape or portrait mode.
  • The lazy Bracket's clamp is also wide enough to be clipped on to almost any desk edge, headboard, wall cabinet or chair.
  • Now watch movies/videos, listen to music on the bed without holding your phone from this incredible flexible arm from different angles and distance. This universal mount holder is ideal for holding your mobile device on bed, desk, car, beside sofa
  • Max length: 700mm / 27.5inch wide

name: BLUEDIO H-Turbine Bluetooth 4.1 Wireless stereo headphone headset -White
short_description:
Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H Bluetooth 4.1 wireless stereo
headset has been created after extensive research. Bluedio has found
that current headphones on the market have lots of common defects, such
as serious noise, flat sound, stuffy appearance, etc. For these reasons,
after 3 years of R&D, Bluedio have come up with the Bluedio Turbine
Hurricane H headset.



The Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H headset is compatible with iOs,
android, and windows. Conic powerful bass resonance, 57mm ultra-large
dynamic drivers, turbine style housing, and Bluedio's iconic surging
low-frequency shock let you feel deep bass resonance for superior sound
quality. Ultra-long operation and carefree calling from Bluetooth
4.1with the robust high speed CPU of Bluetooth 4.1 operating system, the
Bluedio Turbine Hurricane H boasts a long usage time of 40 hours of
music, 45 hours talk time, and 1625 hours (approximately 67 days)
standby time. Acoustic echo cancellation and noise reduction reduce
ambient noise while speaking.



Customized function audio sharing allows you to connect to another H
headset via an audio cable, and share music with your friends, it is
recommended that headphones with impedance of 32 or higher be used.
Simultaneously connect two Bluetooth devices, connect with your phone
and tablet seamlessly, and listen to music as you please



Product Features



  • Bluetooth wireless stereo headset
  • 57 mm Ultra lasge dynamic drivers
  • Connect to other H headset via an audio cable

Product Details



  • Brand: Bluedio
  • Model: Turbine Hurricane H
  • Color: White
  • Type: Over the Ear
  • Connectivity: Bluetooth
  • Usage: 40 hours of music, 45 hours of talktime, 1625 hours standby

name: Bluedio Air Fashion Bluetooth Headset - Black
short_description:
Remain immune to annoying external noise while listening to music via this Bluedio Air Fashion Bluetooth Headset that is available in a classy black color. It features random letter as decorations and has a simple contour. The headset supports 4.1 chip that lets you play music wirelessly with most of the smartphone brands. With a long standby time of 1100 hours, you can listen to music or talk for up to 25 hours continuously. The body of this Bluedio Bluetooth headset is constructed out of tough PC material with soft PU leather cover. Adding the fun element in this headset, is the ability to let you answer calls, play or pause music with just a click of a button. Plus, its acoustic echo cancellation makes for clear audio output when attending calls, even when on a busy or crowded road. All of these features, and much more, make the Bluedio headset reviews highly favorable.

Key Features

Bluetooth

Frequency response: 15Hz~25KHz

Micro USB

Sensitivity: 110dB

Superior Sound

This wireless headset by Bluedio is built in with a 24bit HD chip that helps deliver real Hi Fi surround sound. You get a deep bass, high range, and natural vocals, which together provide the ultimate audio experience. The headset comes with a 57mm driver unit that delivers high end audio output.

Comfort First

The Bluetooth Music Headset is sturdy enough to handle your rigorous lifestyle without wilting. Its headband is made out of high toughness PC material with soft PU Leather cover. It's highly flexible and can also be folded. This on ear headset has soft memory sponge fillings that ensure complete comfort during prolonged listing hours. This, in turn, facilitates a comfortable and customized fit.

Button Remote and Mic

Offering complete convenience while traveling is the intelligent control audio cable, which has an anti winding wire. It adopts acoustic echo cancelation, a technology that helps cancel echo and deliver clear calls. This control cable also lets you play or pause music with just a single click.

name: Bluedio M2 Sport Bluetooth Headset - White
short_description:
The Bluedio M2 Sport Bluetooth Headset provides excellent flexibility and does a fine job of delivering quality audio. They are the perfect choice for those who spend most of their time working out or engaging in vigorous physical activity. This headset lets you concentrate and enjoy your exercise with good sound that keeps you motivated. The Bluedio M2 Sports headset is light in weight and easy to carry. It adopts a sweatproof construction that effectively prevents sweat from damaging your speakers. The headset incorporates exclusive HD drivers that deliver crystal clear sound at all times. The Bluedio M2 Bluetooth 4.1 low energy technology doubles your play time by up to 10 hours and lets you go wireless with style. Plus, the built in mic facilitates clear phone calls. The streamlined design of this headset is styled to make usage more comfortable and convenient.

Key Features

Bluetooth 4.1

20Hz-20kHz

Workouts Made Fun!

The Bluedio M2 wireless headset has made its mark in the headphones industry with its high end features. The Bluedio M2 reviews found online are proof of the device's superior performance. It adopts Bluetooth v4.1 low energy technology that lets you listen to music for hours while its ultra light design makes it comfortable enough for prolonged usage. You can have handsfree calls via the built in mic that transfers your voice across clearly. The headset offers a standby time of up to 180 hours and talk or music playtime of around 10 hours.

Look Sporty

The Bluedio M2 specs lead the way with a sleek and slender design. It incorporates an in ear design with unique ear tips that keep the earbuds securely in place. Plus, the control unit is lighter and smaller. This particular headset dons a white color that adds a zing to your workout outfits.

name: Bluedio BS-3 Portable Bluetooth Speakers 3D Neodymium Magnets 10W/52mm Ultra-big Drives/Mic (Silver)
short_description:
Take your music to places it's never been before with this small and light Bluetooth Speakers that have a great capability made to please demanding users looking for wireless speakers with several high tech features and audio technologies.

The Bluedio BS-3 Bluetooth speaker delivers full, natural sound with deeper bass than you would expect from an ultra-compact speaker that fits in the palm of your hand. It connects wirelessly to your smartphone, tablet or other Bluetooth device, so you can listen to your music, videos or games anytime, anywhere. The built-in speakerphone lets you take calls out loud, too.

Bluedio BS-3 has a minimalist design for sleek simplicity and fits for your modern house. With only 0.64 kg of weight, it is light enough to be carried on your travel. Speaker in the front side is covered by a full tiny grill which is designed well. On the top part, there’s a tactile button that is connected with the audio navigation: volume up and down, 3D button, Mute, and power button. The port micro USB to charge the battery and the line-in port are placed on the right side. There’s rubber on the bottom of the speaker to prevent it from slipping.

You might not expect sound this rich from a speaker this small, but the Bluedio BS-3 is something different. You do not have to sacrifice performance for portability. Bluedio BS-3 is equipped with 24 bits HD Hi-Fi DSP, so that the Hi-Fi audio HD decoding can be run in this speaker with a high speed, 24 bits at 48 KHz. The HD music fans are going to love its detail and clear HD sound.

Bluedio BS-3 also adopted dual innovative Neodymium 3-magnet 52mm, which placed on each of the Ultra-big drivers to produce a better bass sound and a clearer full-range sound from its dual radiators. The other interesting feature is the 3D surround effect, which can produce an amazing 3D Surround. This is great for movies, the sound is reproduced exactly as recorded. By clicking the 3D surround effect button, you will get a fantastic sound experience.&

An excellent portable speaker should be backed up by a good battery. Bluedio BS-3 rechargeable lithium-ion battery delivers up to 5 hours of playtime, because it is supported by Bluetooth 4.1, which can save more power than Bluetooth 4.0. If it’s not used, Bluedio BS-3 can standby 1000 hours. At home, you can listen indefinitely by keeping the unit on the charging cradle. The battery charges as you listen and the speaker is always ready to grab to enjoy and share your music on the go, everywhere you go!

The Bluetooth device can be connected from 10m away, so you can enjoy the sound you want without wires. Voice prompts talk you through pairing, making it easier than ever with no code/pin needed, and it remembers the most recent devices you've used, so reconnecting is even simpler. If there is a phone call coming while you are connecting your smartphone to Bluedio BS-3, you can pick up the call and hear a clear audio from the speaker with an acoustic echo cancellation technology. You will get 2 cables with it: micro USB for recharging the battery, and double head 3.5mm Aux-in cable if you want to plug your device without Bluetooth.

Product description:
  1. Innovative Neodymium 3-magnet drivers: Breaking traditional single-magnet construction, 2 more secondary magnets are added to each driver, to greatly improve sensitivity and fidelity. This exclusive technology combines with dual radiators to deliver full-range sound.&
  2. 24bit@48KHz high resolution: To clearly reproduce details, the DSP processor decodes signals at high speed, up to 24bit@48KHz. Let you hear new details even in your most-played favorites.&
  3. 3D surround effect: Simply turn on the 3D surround effect, you'll experience something new - the sound is reproduced exactly as recorded.&
  4. Long-lasting battery life: For great performance, the speaker needs a lot of energy, posting a big challenge to good battery life. Bluedio engineers combine the Latest Bluetooth 4.1 technology and optimized circuit design to ensure 5 hours playback and 1000 hours standby.
  5. Charging time: 3-4 hours for full charge.
  6. Carefully well-built: From the R&D to manufacture, Bluedio inspect every single part to make sure that they are beautifully integrated with each other.&
  7. Support Bluetooth and Line-in
  8. Bluetooth version: V4.1, Profiles: A2DP, AVRCP, HSP, HFP
  9. Bluetooth range up to 10 meters
  10. Built-in microphone so you can enjoy hands-free calling
  11. Support call back the last dialing number&
  12. Speaker size: 22x7.4x6.8cm
  13. Weight: 0.64Kg
  14. Silver color
  15. CE, RoHS, FCC certified
Technical Specifications:
  • Output/RMS: 5W*2
  • Impedance: 16Ohm
  • Battery: Built-in rechargeable 3000mAh Lithium-Ion
  • Input voltage: 1V
  • 3.5mm stereo input for wired connection
  • Frequency: 20HZ-20KHZ
  • SNR: 95db
  • THD: 0.1%
  • Speaker: 52mm 16 5W*2pcs&
What's in the box:
  • 1x Bluedio BS-3 (Silver) Bluetooth Speaker
  • 1x USB Charging Cable
  • 1x Audio 3.5mm Auxiliary Cable
  • 1x User Manual
